  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要建模一个平台资源分配系统。核心概念有六个：Utilisateur作为入口控制器，Plateforme作为Etcd集群，Parrain作为Redis缓存，Porteur和Projet作为工作节点，还有Adresse也是Etcd集群。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Utilisateur",
        "Plateforme",
        "Parrain",
        "Porteur",
        "Projet",
        "Adresse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，方向是从下往上（BT）。我注意到Utilisateur和Plateforme都是基础设施组件，但角色不同——一个是IngressController，一个是EtcdCluster。Parrain作为Redis缓存，它和Plateforme之间是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Utilisateur",
        "Plateforme",
        "Parrain"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Parrain可以被多个Plateforme引用，但每个Plateforme最多只有一个Parrain。用0..*对0..1的依赖关系。同时Parrain也和Adresse有一对一或零的关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Parrain",
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了Parrain到Plateforme的依赖（0..* ← 0..1），以及Parrain到Adresse的关联（0..1 — 0..1）。现在处理Projet和Porteur，它们都是Infra_WorkerNode吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Parrain",
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse",
        "Projet",
        "Porteur"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "只有Projet是WorkerNode，Porteur是EtcdCluster。Projet可以依赖多个Parrain，但Parrain不直接拥有Projet——等等，让我重新理清：Parrain可以被多个Projet依赖，所以是Parrain ← Projet的0..*对0..1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Projet",
        "Parrain",
        "Porteur"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Parrain到Projet的依赖（0..1 ← 0..*）。Porteur作为EtcdCluster，它和Plateforme的关系是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Parrain",
        "Projet",
        "Porteur",
        "Plateforme"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Porteur和Plateforme是多对一的关系：一个Plateforme可以有多个Porteur，但每个Porteur只属于一个Plateforme。另外Porteur和Adresse是一对一关联，Porteur和Projet也是一对一或零的依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Porteur",
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse",
        "Projet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Porteur到Plateforme是0..* ← 0..1，Porteur到Adresse是0..1 — 0..1，Porteur到Projet是0..1 ← 0..1。这样Porteur既关联Adresse又依赖Projet，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Porteur",
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse",
        "Projet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Porteur作为Etcd集群，需要地址（Adresse），同时可以承载一个Projet。最后还有Utilisateur：它也关联Adresse，并且依赖Plateforme。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Utilisateur",
        "Adresse",
        "Plateforme"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Utilisateur到Adresse的关联（0..1 — 0..1），以及Utilisateur到Plateforme的依赖（0..* ← 0..1）。现在检查Plateforme本身：它也需要关联Adresse吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Utilisateur",
        "Adresse",
        "Plateforme"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Plateforme作为Etcd集群也需要Adresse，一对一或零的关联。另外我注意到之前Parrain到Adresse的关系，确认是双向关联不是依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse",
        "Parrain"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。已添加Plateforme到Adresse的关联（0..1 — 0..1）。现在所有关系都建立了：Parrain、Porteur、Utilisateur、Plateforme各自关联Adresse；Parrain被Plateforme和Projet依赖；Porteur被Plateforme依赖且依赖Projet；Utilisateur被Plateforme依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse",
        "Parrain",
        "Porteur",
        "Utilisateur",
        "Projet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查完毕，结构正确。这个模型清晰展示了平台层（Plateforme）如何协调Parrain缓存、Porteur集群和Projet工作节点，以及Utilisateur作为入口的统一地址管理。",
